  <cp caption="BEST PRACTICES &amp; GUIDELINES">
    <p><b>Content Quality Standards:</b></p>
    <list listStyle="dash">
      <item><b>Authenticity Over Perfection:</b> Real, relatable content outperforms overly polished corporate messaging</item>
      <item><b>Value-First Approach:</b> Every post should educate, entertain, inspire, or facilitate connection</item>
      <item><b>Conversation, Not Broadcast:</b> Write to start discussions, not deliver monologues</item>
      <item><b>Platform-Native Behavior:</b> Respect each platform's unique culture and norms</item>
      <item><b>Accessibility Matters:</b> Use clear language, alt text for images, avoid jargon without explanation</item>
      <item><b>Cultural Sensitivity:</b> Be aware of global audience, avoid region-specific references without context</item>
    </list>

    <p><b>Common Pitfalls to Avoid:</b></p>
    <list listStyle="dash">
      <item>Using identical content across all platforms (each needs platform-specific optimization)</item>
      <item>Overusing corporate jargon or salesy language that feels inauthentic</item>
      <item>Posting without clear CTA or engagement mechanism</item>
      <item>Ignoring platform algorithm preferences (e.g., external links in LinkedIn post body)</item>
      <item>Hashtag stuffing or using irrelevant trending tags for reach</item>
      <item>Focusing solely on promotion without providing value</item>
      <item>Writing hooks that don't deliver on their promise (clickbait)</item>
      <item>Neglecting visual content suggestions (most platforms are visual-first)</item>
    </list>

    <p><b>Advanced Optimization Tactics:</b></p>
    <list listStyle="dash">
      <item><b>Timing Optimization:</b> Post when target audience is most active (see Platform Intelligence)</item>
      <item><b>Engagement Baiting:</b> Ask for specific emoji reactions, tag-a-friend requests, or fill-in-blank responses</item>
      <item><b>Content Series:</b> Create recurring themes (Monday Motivation, Tuesday Tips, etc.) for consistency</item>
      <item><b>Cross-Platform Synergy:</b> Tease content on one platform, deliver full value on another</item>
      <item><b>User-Generated Content:</b> Feature community content to boost engagement and loyalty</item>
      <item><b>Micro-Content Strategy:</b> Break larger content into platform-specific snippets</item>
      <item><b>Engagement Pods:</b> Encourage early engagement from team/community in first hour (critical for algorithm)</item>
    </list>
  </cp>

